// Pyrope reference for array_selfref.v: `z = a_0 ^ a_1` (substituting
// vec[0]=a_0 into vec[1]'s expression -- see the .v header for why the
// literal Verilog shape is NOT actually cyclic). KNOWN BROKEN:
// prp-v2prp-array_selfref currently REFUTES (a concrete counterexample, not
// a timeout/inconclusive) -- see small_todo_working.md "Type C".
comb top(a_0:u2, a_1:u2) -> (z:u2) {
  z = a_0 ^ a_1
}
